d 'Usefulness'\n | journal = [[BYU Studies]]\n | volume = 9\n | issue = 3\n | year = 1969\n | pages = 321\u201340\n | url = https://byustudies.byu.edu/content/reverend-george-lane-good-gifts-much-grace-and-marked-usefulness\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Pratt\n | first = Orson\n | author-link = Orson Pratt\n | title = A Interesting Account of Several Remarkable Visions, and of the Late Discovery of Ancient American Records\n | place = Edinburgh\n | publisher = Ballantyne and Hughes\n | year = 1840\n | url = http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/u?/NCMP1820-1846,325\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Quinn\n | first = D. Michael\n | author-link = D. Michael Quinn\n | title = Early Mormonism and the Magic World View\n | publisher = [[Signature Books]]\n | edition = 2nd\n | year = 1998\n | origyear = 1987\n | isbn = 1-56085-089-2\n | title-link = Early Mormonism and the Magic World View\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Quinn\n | first = D. Michael\n | authorlink = D. Michael Quinn\n | contribution = Joseph Smith's ''Experience'' of a Methodist 'Camp-Meeting' in 1820\n | title = Dialogue Paperless: E-Paper #3, Expanded Version (Definitive)\n | publisher = [[Dialogue: A Journal of Mormon Thought]]\n | date = December 20, 2006\n | url = http://www.dialoguejournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/QuinnPaperless.pdf\n | access-date = April 18, 2011\n | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110927235221/http://www.dialoguejournal.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/04/QuinnPaperless.pdf\n | archive-date = September 27, 2011\n | url-status = dead\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Ray\n | first = Craig N.\n | title = Joseph Smith's History Confirmed\n | publisher = [[Foundation for Apologetic Information & Research]]\n | year = 2002\n | url = http://www.fairlds.org/pubs/jshist.pdf\n | url-status = dead\n | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070621132711/http://www.fairlds.org/pubs/jshist.pdf\n | archivedate = June 21, 2007\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Riley\n | first = I. Woodbridge\n | title = Th