Psychological Study of Joseph Smith, Jr.\n | year = 1903\n | url = https://www.google.com/books?id=RrXeHEcJ8roC\n | publisher = Dodd, Mead & Co.\n | place = New York\n}}\n*{{Citation\n | editor-last = Roberts\n | editor-first = B. H.\n | editor-link = Brigham Henry Roberts\n | title = History of the Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints\n | volume = 1\n | publisher = [[The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints]]\n | year = 1902\n | url = https://books.google.com/?id=sx3s_H3seGAC\n}}. See also: [[History of the Church (Joseph Smith)|History of the Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints]]\n*{{Citation\n | last = Shipps\n | first = Jan\n | authorlink = Jan Shipps\n | year = 1985\n | title = Mormonism: The Story of a New Religious Tradition\n | location = Urbana, Illinois\n | publisher = University of Illinois Press\n | isbn = 0-252-01159-7\n | url-access = registration\n | url = https://archive.org/details/mormonismstoryof00ship\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Smith\n | first = Joseph\n | author-link = Joseph Smith\n | chapter = History of the Life of Joseph Smith\n | year = 1832\n | chapter-url = http://en.wikisource.org/w/index.php?title=History_of_the_Life_of_Joseph_Smith&oldid=314384\n | editor-last = Jessee\n | editor-first = Dean C\n | editor-link = Dean C. Jessee\n | title = Personal Writings of Joseph Smith\n | place = Salt Lake City\n | publisher = [[Deseret Book]]\n | isbn = 1-57345-787-6\n | url = http://deseretbook.com/personalwritings\n | publication-date = 2002\n | url-status = dead\n | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081120090052/http://deseretbook.com/personalwritings/\n | archivedate = November 20, 2008\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Smith\n | first = Joseph\n | author-link = Joseph Smith\n | chapter = Diary of Joseph Smith, Jr.\n | year = 1835\n | chapter-url = http://en.wikisource.org/w/index.php?title=Diary_of_Joseph_Smith%2C_Jr._%281835-1836%29&oldid=340992\n | editor-last = Jessee\n | editor-first = Dean C\n | editor-link = Dean C. Jessee\n | title = Personal Writings of Joseph Smith\n | place = Salt Lake City\n | publisher = [[Deseret Book]]\n | isbn = 1-57345-787-6\n | url = http://deseretbook.com/personalwritings\n | publication-date = 2002\n | url-status = dead\n | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081120090052/http://deseretbook.com/personalwritings/\n | archivedate = November 20, 2008\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Smith\n | first = Joseph\n | title = History of the Church\n | date = April 1838}}, copied to {{Citation\n | last1 = Smith\n | first1 = Joseph\n | author1-link = Joseph Smith\n | last2 = Mulholland\n | first2 = James\n | last3 = Thompson\n | first3 = Robert B.\n | last4 = Phelps\n | first4 = William W.\n | author4-link = W. W. Phelps (Mormon)\n | last5 = Richards\n | first5 = Willard\n | author5-link = Willard Richards\n | year = 1839\u20131843\n | chapter = History of the Church, Ms. A\u20131\n | editor-last = Jessee\n | editor-first = Dean C\n | editor-link = Dean C. Jessee\n | title = Personal Writings of Joseph Smith\n | publisher = Deseret Book\n | location = Salt Lake City\n | publication-date = 2002\n | isbn = 1-57345-787-6\n | chapter-url = http://en.wikisource.org/w/index.php?title=History_of_the_Church/A-1&oldid=399581\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Smith\n | first = Joseph\n | author-link = Joseph Smith\n | title = Church History [Wentworth Letter]\n | journal = [[Times and Seasons]]\n | volume = 3\n | issue = 9\n | pages = 706\u201310\n | date = 1 March 1842a\n | format = PDF\n | url = http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/u?/NCMP1820-1846,9801\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Smith\n | first = Joseph\n | author-link = Joseph Smith\n | title = History of Joseph Smith\n | journal = [[Times and Seasons]]\n | volume = 3\n | issue = 10\n | pages = 726\u201328\n | date = 15 March 1842b\n | url = http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/u?/NCMP1820-1846,9815\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Smith\n | first = Joseph\n | author-link = Joseph Smith\n | title = History of Joseph Smith\n | journal = [[Times and Seasons]]\n | volume = 3\n | issue = 11\n | pages = 748\u201349\n | date = 1 April 1842c\n | url = http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/u?/NCMP1820-1846,9825\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Smith\n | first = Lucy Mack\n | author-link = Lucy Mack Smith\n | title = Biographical Sketches of Joseph Smith the Prophet, and His Progenitors for Many Generations\n | place = Liverpool\n | publisher = S.W. Richards\n | year = 1853\n | url = http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/cdm/ref/collection/NCMP1820-1846/id/17401\n}}. See also: [[Biographical Sketches of Joseph Smith the Prophet, and His Progenitors for Many Generations]]\n*{{Citation\n | last = Smith \n | first = Lucy Mack \n | author-link = Lucy Mack Smith \n | title = Lucy Mack Smith, History, 1844\u20131845, bk. [1]\n | place = Nauvoo, IL\n | year = 1844\n | url = https://www.josephsmithpapers.org/paper-summary/lucy-mack-smith-history-1844-1845/49\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Smith \n | first = Lucy Mack \n | author-link = Lucy Mack Smith \n | title = Lucy Mack Smith, History, 1845\n | place = Nauvoo, IL\n | year = 1845\n | url = https://www.josephsmithpapers.org/paper-summary/lucy-mack-smith-history-1845/80\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Smith\n | first = William\n | author-link = William Smith (Latter Day Saints)\n | title = William Smith on Mormonism: A True Account of the Origin of the Book of Mormon\n | place = Lamoni, Iowa\n | publisher = [[RLDS Church]]\n | year = 1883\n | url = http://www.olivercowdery.com/smithhome/1883Wilm.htm\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Smith\n | first = William\n | author-link = William Smith (Mormonism)\n | title = The Old Soldier's Testimony\n | journal = [[The Saints' Herald]]\n | volume = 34\n | issue = 39\n | year = 1884\n | pages = 643\u201344\n | url = http://www.sidneyrigdon.com/dbroadhu/IA/sain1882.htm#100484\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Taylor\n | first = John\n | author-link = John Taylor (Mormon)\n | title = How a Knowledge of God is Obtained\u2014The Gospel to the Dead&mdash;Various Dispensations of the Most High to Mankind\u2014Power of the Priesthood\u2014Restoration of the Gospel Through Joseph Smith\u2014Failings of the Saints\u2014Corruptions of the Wicked\n | journal = [[Journal of Discourses]]\n | volume = 21\n | date = December 7, 1879\n | pages = 155\u2013167\n | url = https://archive.org/stream/JoDV21/JoD_v21#page/n161/mode/2up\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Tucker\n | first = Pomeroy\n | authorlink = Pomeroy Tucker\n | title = Origin, Rise and Progress of Mormonism\n | place = New York\n | publisher = D. Appleton\n | year = 1867\n | url = https://books.google.com/?id=resQAAAAIAAJ\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Turner\n | first = Orasmus\n | title = History of the Pioneer Settlement of Phelps and Gorham's Purchase, and Morris' Reserve\n | place = [[Rochester, New York]]\n | publisher = William Alling\n | year = 1851\n | url = http://olivercowdery.com/texts/1851Trn1.htm#turn1851\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | editor-last = Vogel\n | editor-first = Dan\n | editor-link = Dan Vogel\n | title = Early Mormon Documents\n | volume = 1\n | place = Salt Lake City\n | publisher = [[Signature Books]]\n | year = 1996\n | isbn = 1-56085-072-8\n | url = http://signaturebooks.com/2010/02/early-mormon-documents-volume-one/\n | url-status = dead\n | archiveurl = https://archive.today/20130202040935/http://signaturebooks.com/2010/02/early-mormon-documents-volume-one/\n | archivedate = 2013-02-02\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | editor-last = Vogel\n | editor-first = Dan\n | editor-link = Dan Vogel\n | title = Early Mormon Documents\n | volume = 2\n | place = Salt Lake City\n | publisher = [[Signature Books]]\n | year = 1998\n | isbn = 1-56085-093-0\n | url = http://signaturebooks.com/2010/02/early-mormon-documents-volume-two/\n | url-status = dead\n | archiveurl = https://archive.today/20130202201755/http://signaturebooks.com/2010/02/early-mormon-documents-volume-two/\n | archivedate = 2013-02-02\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | editor-last = Vogel\n | editor-first = Dan\n | editor-link = Dan Vogel\n | title = Early Mormon Documents\n | volume = 3\n | place = Salt Lake City\n | publisher = [[Signature Books]]\n | year = 2000\n | isbn = 1-56085-133-3\n | url = http://signaturebooks.com/2010/02/early-mormon-documents-volume-three/\n | url-status = dead\n | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110810231726/http://signaturebooks.com/2010/02/early-mormon-documents-volume-three/\n | archivedate = 2011-08-10\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | editor-last = Vogel\n | editor-first = Dan\n | editor-link = Dan Vogel\n | title = Early Mormon Documents\n | volume = 4\n | place = Salt Lake City\n | publisher = [[Signature Books]]\n | year = 2002\n | isbn = 1-56085-159-7\n | url = http://signaturebooks.com/2010/02/early-mormon-documents-volume-four/\n | url-status = dead\n | archiveurl = https://archive.today/20130202130344/http://signaturebooks.com/2010/02/early-mormon-documents-volume-four/\n | archivedate = 2013-02-02\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | editor-last = Vogel\n | editor-first = Dan\n | editor-link = Dan Vogel\n | title = Early Mormon Documents\n | volume = 5\n | place = Salt Lake City\n | publisher = [[Signature Books]]\n | year = 2003\n | isbn = 1-56085-170-8\n | url = http://signaturebooks.com/2010/02/early-mormon-documents-volume-five/\n | url-status = dead\n | archiveurl = https://archive.today/20130202055032/http://signaturebooks.com/2010/02/early-mormon-documents-volume-five/\n | archivedate = 2013-02-02\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Vogel\n | first = Dan\n | author-link = Dan Vogel\n | title = Joseph Smith: The Making of a Prophet\n | year = 2004\n | place = Salt Lake City\n | publisher = Signature Books\n | isbn = 1-56085-179-1\n | title-link = Joseph Smith: The Making of a Prophet\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Waite\n | first = David Nye, Sr.\n | title = The Prairies, Nauvoo, Joseph Smith, the Temple, the Mormons &c\n | date = August 30, 1843\n | newspaper = Pittsburgh Gazette\n | url = http://www.sidneyrigdon.com/dbroadhu/PA/penn1842.htm#091543\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Widmer\n | first = Kurt\n | year = 2000\n | title = Mormonism and the Nature of God: A Theological Evolution, 1833-1915\n | location = Jefferson, NC\n | publisher = [[McFarland & Company]]\n | isbn = 0-7864-0776-X\n}}.\n{{Refend}}\n==Further reading==\n*{{citation\n | url = http://publications.maxwellinstitute.byu.edu/fullscreen/?pub=1458&index=13\n | title = Asked and Answered: A Response to Grant H. Palmer\n | authorlink = James B. Allen (historian)\n | first = James B.\n | last = Allen\n | year = 2004\n | journal = [[FARMS Review]]\n | volume = 16\n | issue = 1\n | pages = 235\u2013285\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Backman\n | first = Milton\n | author-link = Milton V. Backman\n | title = Joseph Smith's First Vision: Confirming Evidences and Contemporary Accounts\n | edition = Revised and enlarged 2nd\n | location = Salt Lake City, Utah\n | publisher = [[Bookcraft]]\n | year = 1980\n | isbn = 0884943992\n | oclc = 6878369\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | last = Brown\n | first = Matthew B.\n | author-link = Matthew B. Brown\n | title = A Pillar of Light: The History and Message of the First Vision\n | location = American Fork, Utah\n | publisher = [[Covenant Communications]]\n | year = 2009\n | isbn = 978-1598117950\n | oclc = 320143246\n}}.\n*{{Citation\n | editor-last = Dodge\n | editor-first = Samuel Alonzo\n | editor2-last = Harper\n | editor2-first = Steven\n | editor2-link = Steven C. Harper\n | title = Exploring the First Vision\n | url = https://rsc.byu.edu/recent-books/exploring-first-vision\n | location = Provo, Utah\n | publisher = [[Religious Studies Center]], [[Brigham Young University]]\n | year = 2012\n | isbn = 978-0842528184\n | oclc = 794272136\n}}.\n*{{citation\n | chapter-url = http://www.utlm.org/onlinebooks/changech6.htm\n | chapter = Chapter 6: The First Vision\n | authorlink = Jerald and Sandra Tanner\n | first = Jerald and Sandra\n | last = Tanner\n | title = The Changing World of Mormonism\n | year = 1981\n | origyear = 1979\n